m><item><title><![CDATA[Galaxy Z Fold 5 review: Five years in, Samsung is treading water]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> 2019 年，三星发布了<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-04-22-samsung-galaxy-fold-review-expensive-experiment.html">初代 Galaxy Fold</a> ，这是第一款配备柔性显示屏的手机（不包括<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-01-07-royole-flexpai-hands-on.html">Royole Flexpai</a>等冒牌产品）。尽管它有很多缺陷，但你还是可以看到它的潜力。在接下来的几年里，三星通过 IPX8 防水、更耐用的设计和原生手写笔支持等改进了其旗舰可折叠产品。然而，最近，随着更多的迭代改进和更少的重大升级来填写规格表，创新的步伐开始放缓。新款 Galaxy Z Fold 5 上也有类似的情况：虽然它的许多升级（包括更亮的主屏幕）很不错，但也有点多余。即使是 2023 年的一项重大变化——三星的新型 Flex 铰链——也并没有真正改变你使用设备的方式；它只是改变了你使用设备的方式。它只是让它变得更薄一点。当你考虑到价格仍然维持在 1,800 美元时，感觉三星的 Z Fold 系列——甚至整个类别——正在失去动力。</p><h2>设计与展示</h2><p>Z Fold 5 与其前代产品基于相同的基本蓝图构建。它有一个细长但很高的外部覆盖屏幕，打开后可以看到一个大的主显示屏，电源按钮内置有指纹传感器。今年的主要变化是三星的 Flex 铰链，它基于两轨内部结构，不仅比以前更小，而且还消除了关闭时手机之间的间隙。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="4aa6cc12645b44bcbdebe4107e9c311c"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/33VUwr7Ow3Y" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><p><core-commerce id="d101c717cb27409584b0af6a813417a6" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>这是 Z Fold 用户自最初以来一直要求的。除了将手机厚度缩小至仅 13.4 毫米之外，消除这个间隙还可以减少灰尘或岩石进入内部并损坏精美的柔性屏幕的机会。但这还不是全部。三星表示，其 Flex 铰链创造了一种新的水滴形折痕，可以减轻显示屏上的压力，这有利于长期耐用性。它还有助于将工厂安装的屏幕保护膜固定到位，这在<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/z-fold-3-long-term-durability-report-heres-what-samsung-still-cant-get-right-130053466.html">以前的型号</a>上是<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://gizmodo.com/life-with-a-foldable-phone-is-a-game-changer-with-one-t-1847439973">一个问题</a>。</p><p>新的铰链还使该设备的使用和握持更加舒适。当手机关闭时，更薄的铰链更适合您的手，并且打开时也更顺畅。我只是希望没有花费五代人的时间才到达这里。与此同时，三星设法将主显示屏的亮度提高到 1,750 尼特，与 S23 Ultra 相同，并且比 Pixel Fold（1,450 尼特）更亮。因此，虽然谷歌可折叠手机的柔性显示屏很好，但 Z Fold 5 的更好。它的尺寸和方向非常适合阅读电子书或浏览漫画，而且我认为三星的旗舰可折叠设备是玩<em>Marvel Snap 的最佳设备。</em>您仍然可以使用手写笔绘图或做笔记，Z Fold 5 的新型 S Pen 比以前薄 40%。但由于手机内部仍然没有空间在不使用时存放它，因此您可能需要将其与三星新款<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAT6OKEfYbC8NW1legKQ8cTgwNVc_lXNi6uLy610Q945k&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Fmobile%2Fmobile-accessories%2Fphones%2Fgalaxy-z-fold5-slim-s-pen-case-sand-ef-of94pcuegus%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Slim S Pen 保护壳</a>配对。</p><h2>性能和多任务处理</h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/1709cc90-36b6-11ee-bf7f-f4b20ae1aa8d" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="Z Fold 5 的 6.2 英寸保护屏与去年的手机基本相同。" data-uuid="b25a4474-2f60-387e-8abe-2e40bfd651f9"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">摄影：Sam Rutherford/Engadget</div></figure><p>去年的型号一点也不慢，但得益于适用于 Galaxy 芯片的全新 Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 2，Z Fold 5 现在甚至更快。在传统基准测试中，它在 Geekbench 6 中的多核分数明显高于 Pixel Fold（5,362 vs 3,226）。 Z Fold 5 的响应速度令人难以置信，在游戏中、图形和动画都非常流畅。这意味着，如果你是那种无论做什么都需要足够速度的高级用户，那么 Z Fold 5 是比 Pixel Fold 更好的选择，后者的 Tensor G2 芯片为 AI 任务保留了更多的马力。</p><p>三星还通过三种方式提高了移动生产力。为了更快、更轻松地启动并排应用程序模式，新手势可让您用两根手指从屏幕侧面滑入，立即切换到双窗格模式。或者，如果您想将全屏应用程序转换为窗口应用程序，只需从顶部两个角之一沿对角线向下滑动即可。这两种手势都非常方便，使用起来非常轻松。但默认情况下它们并未打开，因此请记住在设置的“高级功能”选项卡中激活它们。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/a5a20650-3640-11ee-b7fb-f8125dcb3592" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="Z Fold 5 的新型 Flex 铰链使三星能够使手机变得更薄，并消除关闭时内部的间隙。" data-uuid="040d4e2f-fc65-3fad-9c53-2c37dba834c0"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">摄影：Sam Rutherford/Engadget</div></figure><p>另一个更新是 Z Fold 5 的任务栏现在最多可以显示四个最近的应用程序，而不是两个。这是一个简单而直接的改变，可以更好地利用 Z Fold 5 大主显示屏的宽度。我唯一的抱怨是扩展的任务栏和添加的手势是软件更新，所以我们不需要全新的设备来获取它们。也就是说，与采用更简化的多任务处理方法的 Pixel Fold 相比，三星的桌面式任务栏仍然是那些想要像 PC 一样使用手机的人的最佳选择。并且不要忘记三星方便的 Dex 模式仍然存在。</p><h2>相机</h2><p>Z Fold 5 与其前身具有相同的成像设置：50MP 主摄像头、12MP 超广角摄像头和 10MP 长焦摄像头（背面具有 3 倍光学变焦），以及主摄像头下方的 10MP 自拍摄像头和 4MP 摄像头展示。在真空中，它们几乎能够在任何环境下拍出一张好照片。然而，当你考虑到<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-review-specs-price-photo-and-video-take-center-stage-140034341.html">S23 Ultra 的</a>成本低 600 美元并配备 200MP 主传感器和 10 倍光学变焦镜头时，这让三星最昂贵的手机处于一个奇怪的位置。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/3a569130-3641-11ee-b9af-39f897b8581e" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="令人失望的是 Galaxy Z Fold 5 的摄像头与其前身基本没有变化。" data-uuid="3e70c8b7-94d3-3c05-852c-a55a30f00803"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">萨姆·卢瑟福/Engadget</div></figure><p>更尴尬的是<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-fold-review-the-challenger-that-samsung-needs-specs-price-170003458.html">Pixel Fold</a>具有更长的变焦（5 倍与 3 倍）和更好的整体图像处理能力。在我的测试中，这使得 Pixel 在各种条件下都成为更熟练的射击者。</p><p>在明亮的光线下，Z Fold 5 拍摄的图像具有三星典型的丰富、饱和的色彩配置。缺点是有时会导致少量细节损失、偶尔出现高光溢出和色调稍微不太准确。与此同时，在低光照条件下，三星的夜间模式在改善曝光方面做得很好，而且没有太多副作用。也就是说，得益于谷歌的夜视功能，Pixel Fold 拍摄的照片通常会更加明亮和清晰。一个很好的例子是我在晚上拍摄的一些花朵，其中 Z Fold 5 的照片拥有更鲜艳的色彩，但缺少花瓣上一些更精细的纹理。</p><core-slideshow data-slideshowid="35a140c4-ed72-4fd0-915f-f6a995f9e290" /><h2>电池寿命</h2><p>尽管电池比 Pixel Fold 更小（4,400 mAh vs 4,800 mAh），但 Z Fold 5 的续航时间更长。在我们的视频测试中，三星手机在使用主显示屏时持续了 19 小时 48 分钟，在使用覆盖屏时持续了令人印象深刻的 23:10。在这两个方面，这都比 Pixel Fold 更好，后者的内屏成绩为 15 分 22 秒，外屏成绩为 22 分 21 秒。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/d4d1cc30-3640-11ee-bdee-af352764bea2" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="Z Fold 5 完全平放的能力听起来并不是一个很大的变化，但这是因为它应该提高耐用性，同时在折叠时减少屏幕上的压力。" data-uuid="ed3612b2-07f9-3825-8e75-241f4b070256"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">摄影：Sam Rutherford/Engadget</div></figure><p> Z Fold 5 的充电速度与 25 瓦有线充电、15 瓦无线充电和 5 瓦电力共享（又称反向无线充电）保持一致。这是可用的，但同样，更便宜的 S23 Ultra 可以做得更好，插入时功率可达 45 瓦。</p><h2>包起来</h2><p>作为一个仍然对可折叠设备持乐观态度并拥有三星最近三代旗舰柔性手机的人，我情不自禁地喜欢Z Fold 5。它更快、更时尚，主显示屏更亮，电池寿命也比以前更长。我纠结的问题是，我们应该真正期待第五代设备有多少调整和更新。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/3df57bb0-36b6-11ee-9af5-a81f23379b9e" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="Z Fold 5 无疑是玩 Marvel Snap 的最佳设备。" data-uuid="ed70ff45-c00f-3a3e-86a7-1cddcbd30fad"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">摄影：Sam Rutherford/Engadget</div></figure><p>自 2019 年最初的概念设备问世以来，Z Fold 5 已经成熟了很多，而三星的新型 Flex Hinge 是像我这样的人一直在等待的一个重要里程碑。但归根结底，这款手机现在能做的事情并不是以前做不到的。只是瘦了一点，就好像老模特在健身房里度过了过去 12 个月一样。由于价格仍然非常高，我认为 Z Fold 5 不足以吸引那些尚未购买可折叠手机的人。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/galaxy-z-fold-5-review- Five-years-in-samsung-is-treading-water-140002461.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/galaxy-z-fold-5-review-five-years-in-samsung-is-treading-water-140002461.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 90062f4b-dbad-4b53-b182-31f5482c3f5b</guid><dc:creator>萨姆·卢瑟福</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 14:00:02 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691589678</ingested><modified> 2023-08-09T14:02:26+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sam Rutherford]]></category><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/7ed28390-36b5-11ee-99f7-480a1f0e0be9" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/7ed28390-36b5-11ee-99f7-480a1f0e0be9" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Photo by Sam Rutherford/Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Samsung's latest flagship ship-- the Galaxy Z Fold 5 -- starts at $1,800 and goes on sale August 11th.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Samsung Galaxy Z Fold 5]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best Xbox games for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在 Xbox One 推出之前，一系列失误让微软排名第二。不过，随着<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwOEg3NVJUWjg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZHMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjBhNmU2ZWRiLTRiMzYtNDI5MC1iNWU1LWE0NGFiYjYwMjRjOCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAdCY1Ouea6Ye_E8ZBLQVFsHtK7IC6Z9AHRQ53QcLI6FU&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB08H75RTZ8">Xbox Series X</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVja2chGXjB4Lqvh7g-yFx643XegWlyGfH9m-TTWFYyP&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB08G9J44ZN%2F">S</a>的推出，微软在竞争中处于有利地位。两者都是价格合理、规格齐全的游戏机，拥有跨越二十年的庞大游戏库。</p><p>微软的游戏机策略是独一无二的。拥有 7 年旧 Xbox One 的用户可以与全新 Xbox Series X 的所有者访问几乎相同的游戏库。这使得为各种游戏机维护有意义的不同列表变得困难 - 至少目前如此。不过，尽管下一代独占游戏可能很少见，据报道，PS4 的销量比 Xbox One 的销量高出二比一，但仍有很多游戏玩家根本没有体验过微软自 2017 年中期以来所提供的大部分内容。 10 年代。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>正是怀着这样的心态，我们制定了这份清单：在长时间远离 Microsoft 后，我​​们会向今天拿起 Xbox 的人推荐哪些最佳游戏（无论是 Series X、Series S、One X 还是 One S）控制台？</p><p>这个列表混合了微软游戏机独有的游戏和在 Xbox 上玩得最好的跨平台游戏。我们已尽力解释 Microsoft 系统在适当的情况下带来的好处。哦，虽然我们知道有些人可能讨厌订阅服务，但绝对值得考虑<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy54Ym94LmNvbS9lbi11cy9nYW1lcy9zdG9yZS94Ym94LWdhbWUtcGFzcy11bHRpbWF0ZS9jZnE3dHRjMGtoczA_IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIwYTZlNmVkYi00YjM2LTQyOTAtYjVlNS1hNDRhYmI2MDI0YzgifQ&amp;signature=AQAAATA7cFPYXyTkpJeNab6R9hJfA-cPdcZE-1KJNU5fwe8R&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xbox.com%2Fen-us%2Fgames%2Fstore%2Fxbox-game-pass-ultimate%2Fcfq7ttc0khs0%3F">Game Pass Ultimate</a> ，它允许您按月付费玩此列表中的许多游戏。</p><h2>死亡循环</h2><p><core-commerce id="ba2699a68b574aebbfe9832c3d0a725c" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <em>《Deathloop》</em> （来自《耻辱》系列的工作室）很容易解释：你被困在不断重演的一天中。如果你死了，你就会回到早晨，再次重复这一天。如果你坚持到一天结束，你仍然会重复一遍。柯尔特必须通过有效地谋杀七个主角来“打破循环”，因为他们永远不会同时出现在同一个地方。它还时尚、方便且有趣。</p><p>当你试图摆脱这个时间异常时，你也会被另一位岛上居民朱莉安娜追捕，她和你一样，能够记住每个循环中发生的一切。她还会阻止你逃离某个区域，并且通常会干扰你逃离时间循环的计划。 （在线多人游戏也很容易让人上瘾，角色互换。你扮演朱莉安娜，追捕柯尔特并挫败他的谋杀计划。）</p><p>当你一次又一次地穿过这些区域时，你将为自己装备增加超自然力量的石板，以及更强大的武器和饰品，以嵌入枪支和你自己中。通过这个，你可以定制你的游戏风格或以最好的方式装备自己，以在朱莉安娜的帮助下生存并完成暗杀。每个时期和区域都会奖励重复探索，包括秘密枪支、与 NPC 的隐藏对话以及大量的世界建设知识等您亲自发现。</p><p> 《死亡循环》最初是 PlayStation 限时独占游戏，于 2022 年 9 月登陆 Xbox。</p><h2>守望先锋2 </h2><p><core-commerce id="3822b786d9ad4315834487174a8c9dbe" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>尽管暴雪这次改善了新玩家的入门通道，<em>但《守望先锋 2》</em>仍然有一个陡峭的学习曲线。不过，坚持下去，你就会沉迷于也许是最好的团队射击游戏中。 <em>《守望先锋 2》</em>的目标看似简单——站在目标上或目标附近，让其他队伍远离目标足够长的时间才能获胜。实际情况要复杂得多。对于未经训练的人来说，比赛可能看起来五彩斑斓的混乱，但<em>《守望先锋 2》</em>的目标看似简单——站在目标上或目标附近，让对方远离对手足够长的时间以获得胜利。</p><p>实际情况要复杂得多。暴雪将每支队伍的玩家人数从六人减少到五人。与原版<em>《守望先锋》</em>相比，再加上全面的角色调整，游戏节奏更快、更有趣。虽然更加强调个人影响，但你仍然需要与队友良好合作才能获得胜利。</p><p>现在拥有超过 30 名英雄，每个英雄都拥有独特的能力和游戏风格，您一定会找到一些可以与您产生共鸣的<em>《守望先锋 2》</em>角色。第一批新英雄都玩起来很刺激。还有许多很棒的（尽管通常相当昂贵）新皮肤可供搭配。得益于暴雪标志性的打磨水平，这款游戏的外观和声音也非常棒。至少在你弄清楚如何玩<em>《守望先锋 2》</em>之前，你会惊叹它的精美外观。</p><h2>埃尔登之环</h2><p><core-commerce id="" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>为什么我们不包括<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAY-rc5BHiScd9EazPcIS1hbKT5FMEEvNJdS1NGHDyK8W&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FElden-Ring-Xbox-One%2Fdp%2FB07SMBNTSJ%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid"><em>《Elden Ring》</em></a> ？ FromSoftware 最新的动作角色扮演游戏有很多优点，但这款游戏最令人印象深刻的是，尽管规模庞大，但它的手工制作感觉却十分出色。 <em>《Elden Ring》</em>虽然很大，但绝对不会让人觉得它在浪费你的时间。离得很远; FromSoftware 创造了一个丰富的开放世界，每个角落都有令人惊讶、令人愉快或完全可怕的东西。我永远不会忘记我发现一个箱子，将我的角色传送到一个充满可怕怪物的洞穴的那一刻。 <em>《埃尔登环》</em>充满了此类发现。</p><p>如果你担心<em>《Elden Ring》的</em>难度会碰壁，不用担心。当然，它可能很难，但它也是 From 迄今为止最容易上手的游戏。如果你觉得战斗过于痛苦，可以选择法师建造并从远处轰炸你的敌人，完成支线任务等等。如果一切都失败了，探索<em>《Elden Ring》</em>世界的奖励之一就是经验，你可以用这些经验来让你的角色变得更强大。</p><h2>控制</h2><p><core-commerce id="9b0646edf9c04eb7ad8836e9a3bdd16e" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>以<em>《心灵杀手》</em>中怪异的<em>《双峰》</em>叙事为例，将其与<em>《量子破碎</em>》的疯狂力量和枪战结合在一起，你就获得了<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhTWjFGNUZCP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLWRzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIwYTZlNmVkYi00YjM2LTQyOTAtYjVlNS1hNDRhYmI2MDI0YzgifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAb-mT1O2eoop_v7mVo5v6CzIKruanvg2dh0vXqu3y2Tg&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08SZ1F5FB"><em>《控制》</em></a> 。扮演一名寻找失踪兄弟的女人，你很快就会发现现实与幻想之间只有一线之隔。对于任何从小就喜欢<em>《X 档案》</em>和超自然现象的人来说，这都是一种猫薄荷。这也是工作室在创意高度上努力的一个典型例子，完善和发展了过去十年主导游戏的开放世界公式。</p><p>对上一代 Xbox 的<em>控制效果</em>好坏参半，One S 稍显吃力，但 One X 在保真度和流畅度方面远远超过 PS4 Pro。随着下一代游戏机的推出，“终极版”出现了，它为游戏机玩家带来了 PC 游戏玩家所享受的光线追踪和更高的帧速率。虽然您只能作为下一代所有者获得这些好处，但它还包括所有已发布的 DLC，并且是我们建议购买的版本，即使您不打算立即升级。</p><h2>死角</h2><p><core-commerce id="441df37818684f368bcb28e8d55f191c" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>这<em>&nbsp;</em> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAWWqf65aJ4uaJUoFOgPil2Yu9WlulNTmwpzVKfhVMEtJ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDead-Space-Xbox-X%2Fdp%2FB0BGW86RBN" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/Dead-Space-Xbox-X/dp/B0BGW86RBN?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid"><em>《死亡空间》重制版</em></a>感觉就像来自凶残的死灵的温暖、多汁的拥抱，我们的意思是尽可能以最好的方式。 <em>《死亡空间》</em>的<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/dead-space-remake-playstation-5-review-160019905.html">2023 版</a>对 2008 年原版游戏的机制进行了改进，并且没有添加任何不必要的现代臃肿内容。重制版具有完整的配音、新的谜题和扩展的故事情节，并引入了零重力能力，使主角艾萨克·克拉克能够以一种超令人满意的方式飞过游戏的各个部分。</p><p>这些新增内容都没有超越游戏的核心循环：<em>停滞、射击、踩踏</em>。艾萨克获得了暂时冻结敌人的能力，并且拿起了各种武器，但他从未感到被压倒；他总是处于危险之中。残缺不全的尸体怪物突然出现在空间站狭窄的走廊里，从阴影中叉腰向艾萨克冲锋，乞求被击落。 <em>《死亡空间》</em>的第一款游戏普及了爆头并不重要的理念，而重制版也秉承了这一理念，但其战斗节奏仍然让人感觉新鲜。</p><p> 2023 版<em>《死亡空间》</em>证明创新的游戏设计是永恒的（等离子切割机也是如此）。</p><h2>光环：无限</h2><p><core-commerce id="f2a6ca46edb7499089e78b6b7aa31a41" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>士官长的最新冒险可能在叙述上没有多大意义，但玩起来确实很有趣。经过 343 Industries 过去十年的努力， <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9IYWxvLUluZmluaXRlLVhib3gtT25lLVN0YW5kYXJkL2RwL0IwN1NMNllZQlc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZHMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjBhNmU2ZWRiLTRiMzYtNDI5MC1iNWU1LWE0NGFiYjYwMjRjOCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAYYvislHANh4z4ZvZjJJxbVtnDXilb8DXfUkFCNI6YBZ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FHalo-Infinite-Xbox-One-Standard%2Fdp%2FB07SL6YYBW"><em>《光环：无限》</em></a>成功地为微软的旗舰系列注入了新的生命，同时也忠于粉丝喜爱的元素。主要战役比以往更加开放，同时还通过值得信赖的抓钩为您提供了新的行动自由。多人游戏模式非常容易让人上瘾（尽管 343 仍然需要加快体验进程），有大量的地图和游戏模式可以防止事情变得过于陈旧。唯一阻碍它伟大的是它令人困惑和脱节的故事，但 Xbox 粉丝现在在大型独占游戏方面并没有太多选择。</p><h2>极限竞速地平线 5 </h2><p><core-commerce id="6fb0108a18314040989918e498d7e890" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAU0yzKlrsheJOfWA1l8p0TFSvflXUxXjwv8p8r3gYqNN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FForza-Horizon-Standard-Xbox-One-X%2Fdp%2FB097MGZ7MY"><em>极限竞速地平线 5</em></a> <em>&nbsp;</em>这是一款极其有深度和复​​杂的赛车游戏，几乎任何人都可以轻松上手并玩。游戏中有数百辆汽车，您可以无休止地调整它们以适应您的驾驶风格，数十条赛道遍布墨西哥美丽的虚构角落。如果你提高难度，一个错误就会毁掉你的整个比赛，而在线竞争也同样激烈。</p><p>但如果您是赛车游戏新手， <em>《极限竞速：地平线 5》</em>在帮助您上手和运行方面表现出色。游戏的介绍可以让您快速了解您将遇到的四种主要比赛类型（街头赛车、越野赛等），并且诸如倒带按钮之类的功能意味着您可以快速消除错误，如果您尝试并转弯太快而无需重新开始跑步。很简单， <em>《极限竞速：地平线 5》</em>是一款精美且有趣的游戏，几乎适合任何技能水平。开始并参加几场比赛并继续你的一天是很容易的，或者你可以投入几个小时试图成为你可能成为的最好的车手。</p><h2>齿轮5 </h2><p><core-commerce id="927d5f351d414152980e31bb527bbbbc" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAb2XnfHobrWv0cDvjyMrn9_lxbM-mgMUtdIVJprVNais&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGears-War-Game-Year-Digital%2Fdp%2FB08TS5X4N7"><em>《战争机器 5》</em></a>尝试了很多事情，但并没有全部成功。不过，如果您是《战争机器》粉丝，这里有很多值得您喜爱的内容。 The cover-shooter gameplay the series helped pioneer feels great, and the campaign, while not narratively ambitious, is well-paced and full of bombastic set pieces to keep you interested. As they stand, the various multiplayer modes are not great, but <em>Gears 5</em> is worth it for the campaign alone.</p><p> It&#39;s also a true graphical showcase, among the best-looking console games around. Microsoft did a great job optimizing for all platforms and use-cases, with high-resolution and ultra-high (up to 120fps on series consoles) frame rates.</p><h2> Nier: Automata </h2><p><core-commerce id="11f5c26099504e87a84367326ec3856d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> It took more than a while to get here, but <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:GameStop;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=ffe106af-8248-4af3-9098-a2d4fd637766&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=GameStop&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAX9W98Q0NTHEAWeBajzQBwNuwCZ1SKPDpIaD8BYL-zoM&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamestop.com%2Fvideo-games%2Fproducts%2Fnier-automata---become-as-gods-edition%2F177795.html%3F"><em>Nier: Automata</em></a> finally arrived on Xbox One in the summer of 2018. And boy, was it worth the almost-18-month wait. Nier takes the razor-sharp combat of a Platinum Games title and puts it in a world crafted by everyone&#39;s favorite weirdo, Yoko Taro. Don&#39;t worry, you can mostly just run, gun and slash your way through the game, but as you finish, and finish and finish this one, you&#39;ll find yourself pulled into a truly special narrative, one that&#39;s never been done before and will probably never be done again. It&#39;s an unmissable experience, and one that feels all the more unique on Xbox, which has never had the best levels of support from Japanese developers.</p><p> On Xbox One X and Series X, you effectively have the best version of Nier: Automata available, short of a <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://steamcommunity.com/groups/SpecialK_Mods/discussions/3/1334600128973500691/">fan-patched</a> PC game. On Series S and One S... not so much, but you do at least get consistent framerates on the Series S and a passable experience on the One S.</p><h2> Ori and the Blind Forest </h2><p><core-commerce id="313443725dac4ee688d52a5a91e2fb39" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Arriving at a time when &quot;Gears Halo Forza&quot; seemed to be the beginning, middle and end of Microsoft&#39;s publishing plans, <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVfTOXgeVH-KtGSKk3-IKOPfNlTEvwQjDHoEfrKOVEgq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FOri-Blind-Forest-Definitive-Xbox-One%2Fdp%2FB01DCA8SF8"><em>Ori and the Blind Forest</em></a> was a triumph. It&#39;s a confident mash of the pixel-perfect platforming popularized by <em>Super Meat Boy</em> , and the rich, unfolding worlds of Metroidvania games. You&#39;ll die hundreds of times exploring the titular forest, unlocking skills that allow you to reach new areas. It looks and sounds great — like, Disney great — and its story, while fairly secondary to the experience, is interesting. Ori might not do much to push the boundaries of its genres, but everything it does, it does so right. Its sequel, <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfTE7WPzcM9M1leeu2EaffZRkeF-CWIxXNuSuGgLlwuu&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FOri-Will-Wisps-Xbox-One%2Fdp%2FB07DJRPZWY"><em>Ori and the Will of the Wisps</em></a> , is very much “more of everything,” so if you like <em>Blind Forest</em> , it&#39;s well worth checking out too.</p><h2> <strong>Pentiment</strong> </h2><p><core-commerce id="edc1d028640f45ab9e1faedd1ab7e3d9" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATMAEflWj7xnd6hMP5TOT5C8-YIcYTo9jpcspo862H8F&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPentiment-Xbox-Windows-Digital-Code%2Fdp%2FB0BHV2QTK4%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid"><em>Pentiment</em></a> <em>&nbsp;</em> is a 2D-adventure-meets-visual-novel set in 16th-century Bavaria. You play as Andreas Maler, a young artist from a well-to-do family who gets caught up in a murder mystery while trying to complete his masterpiece. The game itself hinges on its artwork and writing. Both are remarkable: The former is like a medieval manuscript brought to life, while the latter is at once warm and biting, but always in complete control of what it&#39;s trying to say. What starts as a seemingly straightforward whodunit turns into a sweeping, soulful meditation on the nature of history, power, community and truth itself. Time and again, it subverts the “your choices matter!” promise video games have long tried (and mostly failed) to fulfill. You don&#39;t expect one of Microsoft&#39;s best first-party Xbox games to be a riff on Umberto Eco&#39;s <em>The Name of the Rose</em> , but, well, here we are.</p><h2> <strong>Hi-Fi Rush</strong> </h2><p><core-commerce id="22f4a55e9d914e5c87e5145c963a0c21" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAX8snM38hLpWDif5gnMP-48ek-l8AYTdKMqwPjegrcom&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FHi-Fi-RUSH-Deluxe-Xbox-Digital%2Fdp%2FB0BWH8DKZ2" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/Hi-Fi-RUSH-Deluxe-Xbox-Digital/dp/B0BWH8DKZ2?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid"><em>Hi-Fi Rush</em></a> is a hack-and-slash action game built entirely around its soundtrack. You can move and jump freely, but all of your steps and attacks are timed to the beat of the backing music. If you time your moves right <em>on</em> the beat, you can do more damage and pull off combos. Everything else in the world pulsates and takes action to the same rhythm, from enemy attacks to lights flashing in the background.</p><p> Is this revolutionary?并不真地。 Every hack-and-slasher has a sense of performance and musicality to it; <em>Hi-Fi Rush</em> just makes the subtext explicit. It&#39;s <em>Devil May Cry</em> on a metronome. But it&#39;s fun. Ripping through a room of goons is satisfying in most video games; ripping through them entirely in rhythm, with each dodge and final blow punctuated by a beat, is even more so. It helps that the soundtrack is actually good and that the combat system never punishes you <em>too</em> hard for button mashing in a panic. It also helps that the tone is that of a cel-shaded Saturday morning cartoon, starring a lovable doofus named Chai as he takes on a comically evil megacorp. <em>Hi-Fi Rush</em> has issues – its stages can drag, for one – but it plays like a passion project from the PS3/Xbox 360 era. It has ideas, and its main concern is being a good time.</p><h2> Red Dead Redemption 2 </h2><p><core-commerce id="e4c78b23150048dda39e64ce734e96af" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATibTCIXYz2C1jYubXuCBIXn0nb7Q1Ez7omtNIcEpnPC&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRed-Dead-Redemption-2-Xbox-One%2Fdp%2FB01MAYC1CJ"><em>Red Dead Redemption 2</em></a> is the kind of game no one but Rockstar, the team behind the Grand Theft Auto series, could make. Only when a studio is this successful can it pour millions of dollars and development hours into a game. Rockstar&#39;s simulation of a crumbling frontier world is enthralling and serves as a perfect backdrop to an uncharacteristically measured story. While the studio&#39;s gameplay may not have moved massively forward, the writing and characters of RDR2 will stay with you.</p><p> While Rockstar hasn&#39;t deemed fit to properly upgrade <em>Red Dead Redemption 2</em> for the next-gen yet, Series X owners will at least benefit from the best last-gen (Xbox One X) experience with the addition of improved loading times. The Series S, on the other hand, gets the One S version, but with an improved 30 fps lock and swifter loading.</p><h2>生化危机村庄</h2><p><core-commerce id="7c30a7a48013413cbce2e0e2ef61437b" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9SZXNpZGVudC1FdmlsLVZpbGxhZ2UtWGJveC1YLVN0YW5kYXJkL2RwL0IwOTQ3ODlZUkg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZHMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjBhNmU2ZWRiLTRiMzYtNDI5MC1iNWU1LWE0NGFiYjYwMjRjOCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAfJmstwVEyn8HZv9ZyhLJzF1iav2cmw3ckOJL5JBjx2P&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FResident-Evil-Village-Xbox-X-Standard%2Fdp%2FB094789YRH"><em>生化危机村</em></a>很令人愉快。这是一个伪装成生存恐怖游戏的哥特式童话故事，虽然这代表了该系列的新鲜氛围，但它并不是一个不受欢迎的演变。 《村庄》中的角色和敌人都充满生机——即使他们显然是不死生物——卡普空对吸血鬼、狼人、海洋生物、巨人和令人毛骨悚然的玩偶的概念进行了巧妙的诠释。这款游戏保留了其恐怖、解谜和动作的根源，并且到处都有安布雷拉公司的痕迹。感觉就像开发者很喜欢这个，你也会的。</p><p> A word of caution before you run to buy it, though: This game doesn&#39;t play great on every Xbox. On Series X, things are great: There&#39;s the option to turn on ray-tracing with the occasional frame rate issue, or to keep it off and have perfect 4K/60 presentation. With the Series S, while there is a ray-tracing mode, it&#39;s almost unplayable. With ray-tracing off, the Series S does a decent job, though. The One X&#39;s 1080p/60 mode is also fantastic, although its quality mode feels very juddery. If you own a base Xbox One or One S, though, there&#39;s really no mode that actually feels enjoyable to play.</p><h2> Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice </h2><p><core-commerce id="1c855dbac578431e98cd9742e800faf3" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9TZWtpcm8tU2hhZG93cy1Ud2ljZS1EaWdpdGFsLVN0YW5kYXJkL2RwL0IwN1ozWEw0UVA_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZHMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjBhNmU2ZWRiLTRiMzYtNDI5MC1iNWU1LWE0NGFiYjYwMjRjOCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAWqL_CsEamZZyAf5YVE3vj3hqm-qVYtRphiN8Dd_IvgE&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSekiro-Shadows-Twice-Digital-Standard%2Fdp%2FB07Z3XL4QP"><em>《只狼：影逝二度》</em></a>不仅仅是另一款《黑暗之魂》游戏。 FromSoftware 的武士冒险与既定的模式背道而驰，取而代之的是缓慢、沉重的战斗和哥特式的绝望，取而代之的是潜行、抓钩和快速的剑术。哦，虽然它仍然是一款困难的游戏，但它比《灵魂》游戏更容易上手——你甚至可以暂停它！所有这些更改的结果仍然可以立即被识别为 FromSoftware 标题，但它有自己的东西，而且非常好。</p><p> This is one game that&#39;s really not had a lot of love from its developer or publisher, as, despite the fact next-gen consoles should be easily able to run this game at 60 fps, the Series S is locked to an inconsistently paced 30 fps, while the Series X doesn&#39;t quite hold to 60 either. With that said, it&#39;s more than playable.</p><h2> Lost Judgment </h2><p><core-commerce id="b034ca2c0dd64c65bd41eae2fb8a78c5" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> This is private eye Takayuki Yagami&#39;s <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:GameStop;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=ffe106af-8248-4af3-9098-a2d4fd637766&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=GameStop&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbUclKxTgGXlHAtfLZeZ1icGRYZts0EQCyjo_Nj7NVIJ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamestop.com%2Fvideo-games%2Fproducts%2Flost-judgment---xbox-series-x%2F291075.html%3F">second adventure</a> ; a spin-off of Sega&#39;s popular, pulpy and convoluted Yakuza saga. He lives in the same Kamurocho area, the same yakuza gangs roam the streets, and there&#39;s the very occasional crossover of side-story characters and, well, weirdos. But instead of punching punks in the face in the name of justice or honor, which was the style of Yakuza <em>&nbsp;</em> protagonist Kazuya Kiryu, Yagami fights with the power of his lawyer badge, drone evidence and… sometimes (read: often) he kicks the bad guys in the face.</p><p> The sequel skates even closer to some sort of serialized TV drama, punctuated by fights, chases and melodrama. For anyone that&#39;s played the series before, it treads familiar ground, but with a more serious (realistic) story that centers on bullying and suicide problems in Japanese high schools, which is tied into myriad plots encompassing the legal system, politics and organized crime.</p><p> Yagami has multiple fighting styles to master, while there are love interests, batting cages, mahjong, skate parks and more activities to sink even more hours into. On the PS5, <em>Lost Judgment</em> looks great. Fights are fluid and the recreated areas in Tokyo and Yokohama are usually full of pedestrians, stores and points of interest. While <em>Yakuza Like a Drago</em> n takes the franchise in a new (turn-based, more ridiculous) direction, <em>Lost Judgment</em> retains the brawling playstyle of the Yakuza series, with a new hero who has, eventually, charmed us.</p><h2> Xbox Game Pass Ultimate </h2><p><core-commerce id="137f22a6da5f44dfab7ac111345e22b4" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> We already mentioned this one but it&#39;s difficult to overemphasize how good a deal <a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9YYm94LUdhbWUtUGFzcy1VbHRpbWF0ZS1NZW1iZXJzaGlwL2RwL0IwN1RGUDdKRkg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZHMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjBhNmU2ZWRiLTRiMzYtNDI5MC1iNWU1LWE0NGFiYjYwMjRjOCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAbIx13ZjEsaaH0nMgLx2YYuLdPxuDIBtEKFdsJ-lNDuE&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FXbox-Game-Pass-Ultimate-Membership%2Fdp%2FB07TFP7JFH">Game Pass</a> is for Xbox owners. For $15 a month you get access to a shifting and growing library of games. The company does a good job explaining what new games are coming and going in advance, so you won&#39;t get caught out by a game disappearing from the subscription service just as you&#39;re reaching a final boss. There are 11 games mentioned in this guide, and seven of them are currently available with Game Pass. The full library is broad, and, while Microsoft&#39;s cloud service is still just in beta, you&#39;ll have access to many of the games on your tablet, phone or browser through xCloud at no extra fee.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-xbox-games-140022399.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-xbox-games-140022399.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 0a6e6edb-4b36-4290-b5e5-a44abb6024c8</guid><dc:creator>恩杰特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 13:30:11 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691587812</ingested><modified> 2023-08-09T13:30:27+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Engadget]]></category><media:content height="1240" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/1a78db70-1d1c-11eb-8f7e-21a8e3cff5ce" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1240" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/1a78db70-1d1c-11eb-8f7e-21a8e3cff5ce" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Aaron Souppouris / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Microsoft's new Series X console and its accessories.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Xbox Series X]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Slack's latest redesign has a dedicated DM tab and a Discord-style Activity view]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/slack/">Slack</a> is getting a new look starting today. The service is rolling out a redesign aimed at helping folks stay focused and get things done by streamlining the interface.</p><p> Perhaps the most obvious change is to the sidebar. On the far left, you&#39;ll no longer see a tile for each of your workspaces if you&#39;re logged in to more than one. Those have been collapsed into a single tile, and Slack is using the freed-up space for new navigation options. </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/55aec7b0-2fc3-11ee-b3f7-d62516cbe7a4" style="height:1536px;width:2048px;" alt="Slack screenshot showing the new redesign, featuring an updated left sidebar with Home, DMs, Activity, Later and More buttons." data-uuid="42b817e9-9d5e-33eb-a70a-c96ae75b5c86"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">松弛</div></figure><p>The sidebar now includes buttons for Home, DMs (direct messages), Activity, Later and More sections, along with a search icon and a new Create button. The Home view is much like the Slack you&#39;ll be used to. From here, you&#39;ll be able to access your various channels, unread items, drafts, apps and more.</p><p> It looks like the DMs section will neatly bring together your direct message conversations and make them easier to access. Your DM list will show the most recent message from each chat, and you can choose whether to see only unread messages. </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/7e574200-2fc3-11ee-ade1-ce16ce1d0b05" style="height:1536px;width:2048px;" alt="Slack screenshot showing the new redesign and a direct messages feed" data-uuid="fc73f6f0-997f-31af-acdc-b8f786934f2d"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">松弛</div></figure><p>The Activity feed combines your threads, mentions and reactions into a single view, though each of those has a dedicated tab within the Activity section. The Later section, meanwhile, has tabs for in-progress, completed and archived actions. The More section is where you&#39;ll find tools such as apps and workflows, canvases and huddles.</p><p> As for the Create button, that replaces the draft message option. From here, you can whip up a message, huddle, canvas or new channel. Elsewhere, there&#39;s a new feature that allows you to hover over an icon for one of the dedicated views (ie DMs or Activity) to take a peek at what&#39;s happening without having to drift away from your current task.</p><p> Slack says it&#39;s rolling out some device-specific updates as well. In <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/slack-mobile-app-redesign-224859698.html">the iPhone</a> , iPad and Android apps, you&#39;ll see tiles at the top of the screen that will take you to the likes of your unreads and threads with a single tap. You&#39;ll also be able to swipe through all your unreads and perhaps catch up on things more quickly. Last but not least, Slack is enabling new themes with a more detailed and customizable color scheme.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/slacks-latest-redesign-has-a-dedicated-dm-tab-and-a-discord-style-activity-view-130032154.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/slacks-latest-redesign-has-a-dedicated-dm-tab-and-a-discord-style-activity-view-130032154.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> dc68d3ba-373f-4ea7-810b-e266560acb74</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 13:00:32 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691592859</ingested><modified> 2023-08-09T14:54:24+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="2413" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-08/08724e90-06bc-11ec-bffe-f874b4aa5808" width="3618"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2413" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-08/08724e90-06bc-11ec-bffe-f874b4aa5808" width="3618"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The Slack app icon is displayed on a computer screen, Wednesday, Dec 2, 2020, in Tokyo. In a deal announced Tuesday, Dec. 1, 2020, business software pioneer Salesforce.com is buying work-chatting service Slack for $27.7 billion in a deal aimed at giving the two companies a better shot at competing against longtime industry powerhouse Microsoft. (AP Photo/Kiichiro Sato)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Salesforce Slack]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Patreon creators can now publish subscriber-only podcasts on Spotify]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> At its Stream On event earlier this year, Spotify <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://newsroom.spotify.com/2023-03-08/creator-monetization-make-money-from-podcasts-patreon/">announced a partnership</a> with Patreon that would bring subscriber-only podcasts from the creator platform to its streaming service. Today, <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://newsroom.spotify.com/2023-08-09/patreon-spotify-connect-exclusive-podcast-patron-member-content-in-feed/">that integration launches</a> for all creators and users globally, allowing patrons to listen to exclusive content alongside other episodes on Spotify. If you stumble upon a show that you don&#39;t yet support monetarily, you can get access with a few taps from the show&#39;s page inside the streaming app.</p><p> Patreon podcasters only need to sync their account with Spotify to get started. Afterwards, all patron-exclusive content will be on a dedicated page on their Spotify show profile. Creators will have the option of adding promotional banners on their free episodes page to help drive subscription numbers. The integration of Patreon is powered by Spotify&#39;s Open Access, which was <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/spotify-podcast-subscription-platform-120040301.html">first announced in 2021</a> . This technology allows shows that host subscription content on other platforms to use their existing log-in credentials to bring those podcasts to the streaming service. Other integrated platforms include Supporting Cast, Supercast and more. Additionally, Spotify has been offering paid podcast subscriptions through its audio production platform Anchor for over two years.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Just like that Anchor setup, any subscriber-only Patreon podcasts that you don&#39;t have access to will show up with a lock icon in the Spotify app. There&#39;s also a small &quot;paid&quot; tag next to the publish date and runtime info. When you tap the lock, a pop up will ask if you want to hear more from the creator before sending you to their Patreon page to view subscription info.</p><p> Spotify doesn&#39;t take a cut of subscriptions that are generated through Open Access. Patreon and Spotify both explain that creators will retain &quot;full control&quot; over their audiences, content and revenue while using the streaming service to expand their reach. There&#39;s no additional cost to integrate Patreon with Spotify either, and creators publishing both free and paid episodes can use the setup.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/patreon-creators-can-now-publish-subscriber-only-podcasts-on-spotify-130016901.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/patreon-creators-can-now-publish-subscriber-only-podcasts-on-spotify-130016901.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 611459d5-18cc-4bde-9bb8-7baf32ee1f43</guid><dc:creator> Billy Steele</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 13:00:16 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691585687</ingested><modified> 2023-08-09T12:54:51+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Billy Steele]]></category><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/1e3e41f0-360f-11ee-87eb-f28cb543ee03" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/1e3e41f0-360f-11ee-87eb-f28cb543ee03" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Spotify/Patreon]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Spotify Patreon]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Spotify Patreon]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best laptops for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>您可能想尽快升级您的技术，但购买新的笔记本电脑可能会让人感到困惑。需要考虑的品牌、功能和配置比以往任何时候都多，而且考虑到我们仍在应对通货膨胀，您可能还会担心价格上涨。好消息是，公司仍在生产大量新笔记本电脑，并且有多种型号供您选择，从经济型 HP Pavilion Aero 13 到可变形的 Microsoft Surface Pro 9，再到我们总体最佳选择的 Apple MacBook空气M2。我们让您轻松挑选最适合您需求的笔记本电脑。</p><h2> What to expect</h2><p>您可能对自己的预算有所了解，但您也知道，如今大多数具有顶级规格的现代笔记本电脑的价格约为 1,800 至 2,000 美元。这并不意味着您找不到 1,000 美元以下的好系统——很多 13 英寸类别的高端超便携式笔记本电脑的基本价格都是 1000 美元，这些笔记本电脑配备了英特尔酷睿 i3 或 i5 系列等芯片。如果价格太贵，您仍然可以选择 600 至 800 美元的价格，但它们可能配备较旧、速度较慢的处理器和调光屏幕。我在这篇最佳笔记本电脑综述中列出了我们最喜欢的经济型笔记本电脑，但我们还有一份<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-budget-laptop-150038435.html">更实惠的笔记本电脑选择</a>列表，您也可以查看。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>在计算出您想要花多少钱后，笔记本电脑的操作系统通常是您首先要缩小的范围。与往常一样，对于喜欢 Apple MacBook 的人来说，做出决定会稍微容易一些。既然该公司已将其 M 系列芯片纳入其整个产品线，您唯一真正需要考虑的是预算、屏幕尺寸以及需要多少电量。</p><p>然而，在 Team Windows 上，向基于 ARM 的芯片的转变并不那么顺利。尽管苹果笔记本电脑能够在使用自己的芯片保持（并且在某些情况下提高）性能的同时大幅延长电池寿命，但 PC 制造商却受到 Windows 缺点的限制。微软去年发布了 Windows 11，它应该在 ARM 驱动的机器上运行得更好。由于第一批笔记本电脑（例如<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lenovo-made-its-first-think-pad-powered-by-a-snapdragon-chip-080035789.html">联想的 ThinkPad X13s</a>或<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lenovo-snapdragon-windows-11-tablet-yoga-laptop-ryzen-virtual-reality-153901587.html">10w 平板电脑</a>）尚未可供评测，因此我们无法判断系统的运行情况。当然，您可以在现有的基于 ARM 的 PC 上升级到 Windows 11，但目前，坚持使用 Intel 或 AMD 处理器仍然更安全。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-08/98e7c4a0-eb92-11ea-b3fb-e2e6726b0a03" alt="戴尔 XPS 13" data-uuid="d57ad901-aed9-3007-829c-5f44dfdef76b"><figcaption>德文德拉·哈达瓦/Engadget</figcaption></figure><p> Let&#39;s not forget there&#39;s a third and fairly popular laptop operating system: Chrome OS.如果您在浏览器中完成大部分工作（大量在线研究、电子邮件和 Google 云端硬盘），那么 Chromebook 可能是一个合适的选择，而且通常更实惠。</p><p>至于购买最好的笔记本电脑时需要注意的其他事项，值得指出的是，今年推出的一些最新型号已经取消了耳机插孔。尽管这似乎还不是一种普遍趋势，但它是一个很好的提醒，请检查机器是否具有您需要的所有连接器（否则，您需要计划购买必要的适配器）。 2022 年的大多数笔记本电脑都提供 WiFi 6 或 6E 以及蓝牙 5.0 或更高版本，如果您有兼容的路由器和设备，这应该意味着更快、更稳定的连接。虽然今年 5G 覆盖范围更加广泛，但您是否需要支持取决于您的旅行次数。</p><p><strong>也可以看看：</strong></p><ul><li><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-laptops-172033838.html"><strong>2023 年最佳游戏笔记本电脑</strong></a></p></li><li><p><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-affordable-windows-laptops-123000512.html"><strong>最便宜的 Windows 笔记本电脑</strong></a></p></li><li><p><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-2-in-1-laptops-173038508.html"><strong>2023 年最佳二合一笔记本电脑</strong></a></p></li><li><p><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-chromebooks-160054646.html"><strong>最好的 Chromebook</strong></a></p></li><li><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-laptops-for-students-130054631.html"><strong>最适合大学生的笔记本电脑</strong></a></p></li></ul><p>您计划将笔记本电脑带到哪里也有助于决定购买的尺寸。去年，许多公司推出了新的 14 英寸笔记本电脑，跨越了超便携笔记本电脑和笨重的 15 英寸笔记本电脑之间的界限。对于大多数人来说，14 英寸屏幕是一个很好的中间立场。但如果您担心重量并想要一台更便携的笔记本电脑，12 或 13 英寸型号会更好。那些想要更强大的处理器和更大的显示屏的人会更喜欢 15 英寸或 16 英寸版本。</p><h2>整体最佳：MacBook Air M2</h2><p><core-commerce id="8eea1a8c234849b6a57ac44c2e9a7f9f" data-type="product-list"></p><p>作为一名 Windows 用户，我发现自己不愿意将 Apple MacBook 称为最佳整体笔记本电脑。但我不能否认苹果向自己的芯片的过渡使其机器变得更好。最新的<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS8yMDIyLUFwcGxlLU1hY0Jvb2stTGFwdG9wLWNoaXAvZHAvQjBCM0JWV0o2WS8_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMnItMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijk5YTdmYjA4LWI0Y2ItMzU5OC04OTBjLTZmNmQ4NzgzMzliMSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAUqS6KibBIOnjTS_t0uCcwZrLnd7hGBpsxxKybHVdU-6&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2F2022-Apple-MacBook-Laptop-chip%2Fdp%2FB0B3BVWJ6Y%2F">MacBook Air M2</a>是 2020 年推出的<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAd5iMhqKO_TuNlRh1GXBTZRBCfJC2lsZDLd35cVd7V4A&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MacBook-13-inch-256GB-Storage%2Fdp%2FB08N5M7S6K">M1</a>的当之无愧的续作，带来了所有用户都会欣赏的全新设计和性能提升。</p><p>这并不是说 M1 是一台运行缓慢的机器——恰恰相反。我们发现它的速度快得令人印象深刻，而<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/macbook-air-m2-review-2022-130040098.html">M2</a>正是建立在这种出色的性能之上。对于 MacBook Air 来说，这可能有点大材小用，但这意味着它可以很好地满足大多数人的工作和娱乐需求。此外，其令人印象深刻的 16.5 小时超长电池续航时间应该足以让任何人完成一天的工作。</p><p>至于它的设计，我们喜欢苹果在这里采取了更均匀的薄型方法，并淘汰了之前型号的楔形形状。 MacBook Air M2 还配备了可爱的 13.6 英寸 Liquid Retina 显示屏，仅被顶部的缺口所干扰，该显示屏装有 1080p 网络摄像头。它的四扬声器设置也是一项改进，所有这些小的硬件变化加起来使机器的外观和感觉与您对其前身的预期更加不同。</p><p>对于那些重视便携性高于一切的人来说，13 英寸 Air 无疑是最佳选择。不过，如果您对稍微大一些的屏幕空间感兴趣，请不要选择<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9hdy9kL0IwQzc2ODYxNjkvP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTJyLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI5OWE3ZmIwOC1iNGNiLTM1OTgtODkwYy02ZjZkODc4MzM5YjEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAUinCg4nIHk5XD9rQaa96mIPpgmlGpj1yku7Ck3uFQt9&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Faw%2Fd%2FB0C7686169%2F">15 英寸 MacBook Air M2</a> 。这款<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-macbook-air-15-inch-review-a-bigger-screen-makes-a-surprising-difference-130033172.html">新款笔记本电脑</a>具有 13 英寸型号的所有优点，同时在仍然纤薄的外形中提供了更大的屏幕。它并没有回避苹果的一个问题，即 RAM 和存储空间比我们希望的基本型号（8GB、256GB SSD）少一点，但这并不能阻止它。它是我们最近使用过的最好的 MacBook 之一，它为 Air 系列的粉丝提供了一个值得考虑的新配置。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/macbook-air-m2-review-2022-130040098.html"><strong>阅读我们对 13 英寸 MacBook Air M2 的完整评测</strong></a></p><h2>最佳 Windows：戴尔 XPS 13 Plus</h2><p><core-commerce id="15e086246a634647b81e0d18af6ffc98" data-type="product-list"></p><p>长期以来，我们最佳 Windows 笔记本电脑的首选一直是戴尔全面的<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Dell;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=b1bb23c9-a2d4-4e4e-bfac-7a560ebe7641&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Dell&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASAyWkI2s05Ra2lkX3olOfFRY0TI8CiN9aUimAjn8B5N&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dell.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Fdell-laptops%2Fxps-13-laptop%2Fspd%2Fxps-13-9315-laptop%2Fxn9315cto030s">XPS 13 系列</a>，对于那些不需要 Mac 的人来说，它仍然是最好的笔记本电脑。是的， <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Dell;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=b1bb23c9-a2d4-4e4e-bfac-7a560ebe7641&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Dell&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdtfaIOzhpL4OnNN_QW15c2ckpfoKACaswmr_O89Y8Sw&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dell.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Fdell-laptops%2Fxps-13-plus-laptop%2Fspd%2Fxps-13-9320-laptop%2Fxn9320cto020s">新款 XPS 13 Plus</a>没有耳机插孔，我们还没有进行测试。但 XPS 13 是一款功能全面的笔记本电脑，并且仍然是目前最好看的电脑之一。</p><p>与前代产品一样，戴尔<a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/dells-xps-13-plus-ultraportable-no-headphone-jack-180043410.html">XPS 13 Plus</a>配备可爱的 OLED 显示屏和令人印象深刻的超薄边框，并配有宽敞舒适的键盘。它还采用了新的简约设计，看起来更现代。我不确定顶部的一排电容键是否取代了传统的功能键，但我相信笔记本电脑的第 12 代英特尔酷睿处理器将比上一型号提供健康的性能提升。</p><p>如果您不确定戴尔对 XPS 13 所做的更改，或者您确实需要耳机插孔，那么老一代仍然是可靠的选择。还有<a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.e