0iIvqGHZ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sony.com%2Fen%2FSonyInfo%2FIR%2Flibrary%2Fpresen%2Fer%2Fpdf%2F23q1_sony.pdf" class="rapid-with-clickid">上调</a>(PDF) 6.1%，因为这些业务的销售额高于预期。它还预计其净利润将比之前的预测高出2.4%，从8400亿日元（58.6亿美元）增至8600亿日元（60亿美元）。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>特别是对于其游戏部门，索尼调整了其预测，因为它预计非第一方<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ps5-cloud-game-streaming-begins-rolling-out-to-beta-testers-190938931.html">PlayStation</a>游戏（包括附加内容）的销量将会增加。 Several much-awaited games are coming out for PlayStation gamers this year, such as <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-spider-man-2-story-trailer-teases-more-venom-more-villains-and-more-drama-040056520.html"><em>Spider-Man 2</em></a> <em>,</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/assassins-creed-mirage-will-arrive-on-october-12-205552847.html"><em>Assassin&#39;s Creed Mirage</em></a> <em>,</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/cyberpunk-2077-phantom-liberty-will-take-you-back-to-night-city-on-september-26th-181652972.html"><em>Cyberpunk 2077: Phantom Liberty Expansion</em></a> <em>,</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/avatar-frontiers-of-pandora-launch-date-sgf-2023-174516354.html"><em>Avatar: Frontiers of Pandora</em></a> <em>&nbsp;</em>和<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ea-sports-fc-24-will-hit-consoles-and-pc-on-september-29th-182429306.html"><em>EA 体育俱乐部</em></a>。</p><p>非第一方游戏销量的预期增长将得益于成本和费用的下降。也就是说，它们也将被“PlayStation 5 硬件盈利能力的恶化”所抵消。索尼最近在全球<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.polygon.com/23802839/ps5-sale-price-drop-sony-playstation">多个地区</a><a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sonys-disc-based-playstation-5-falls-back-to-449-093647320.html">下调了 PS5 的定价</a>。虽然这会导致游戏机的整体收入下降，但也可能会让持观望态度的人们最终购买 PS5，进而可能导致更多的游戏购买。</p><p>值得注意的是，索尼今年第一季度的 PS5 出货量为 330 万台。这几乎是上一季度 630 万台销量的一半，不过这个数字是在假期期间计算的，当时企业的表现通常比平时好。这是索尼迄今为止 PS5 销量表现最好的第一季度， <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-has-sold-over-40-million-ps5-consoles-150040065.html">总销量达到 4170 万台</a>。</p><p>尽管索尼以更好的全年数据调整了展望，但由于智能<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://techcrunch.com/2023/04/18/a-12-decline-in-global-smartphone-shipments-is-what-passes-for-stability-these-days/">手机销量持续下降的趋势，</a>索尼还是降低了对移动传感器销量的预期。尽管<em>《蜘蛛侠：穿越蜘蛛侠宇宙》</em>取得了成功，索尼影业的收入也同比下降。该公司预计业务也不会复苏，并认为由于美国编剧工会和演员工会罢工的影响，其业绩将比去年四月的预测更差。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/sony-raises-its-annual-forecast-on-the-strength-of-its-playstation-sales-113514305.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/sony-raises-its-annual-forecast-on-the-strength-of-its-playstation-sales-113514305.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 24b8c6c6-2589-4bbd-9157-153d253a523d</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 11:35:14 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691588182</ingested><modified> 2023-08-09T13:36:31+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Company Earnings]]></category><category><![CDATA[Investment & Company Information]]></category><category><![CDATA[Finance]]></category><category><![CDATA[Game Consoles]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="2167" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/aef7f710-3694-11ee-bfdf-226aa31429ef" width="3251"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2167" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/aef7f710-3694-11ee-bfdf-226aa31429ef" width="3251"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NurPhoto via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[PlayStation 5 game packaging and PlayStation DualSense controller in the background are seen in this illustration photo taken in Krakow, Poland on April 9, 2022. (Photo by Jakub Porzycki/NurPhoto via Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[PlayStation And Thrustmaster Photo Illustrations]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The Morning After: Voyager 2 is alive!]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>美国宇航局 (NASA) 已<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nasa-regains-contact-with-voyager-2-after-it-went-dark-for-two-weeks-074447578.html"><ins>与旅行者 2 号重新取得联系，</ins></a>这是离开太阳系的两颗人造物体之一。该机构在 7 月 21 日与探测器失去了联系，此前该探测器进行了一系列计划中的演习，使其远离地球两度。它本应在 10 月份重新调整方向，但机构官员不想等那么久才恢复联系。</p><p>旅行者 2 号团队使用地面发射器网络向探测器“喊出”命令，告诉它返回地球。这个大声的命令花了 18.5 个小时才到达该装置，而 NASA 也需要同样长的时间才得知它已经成功。这是人类聪明才智的证明，也是一个重要的提醒，不要错过航海者 2 号发出的每一秒数据，因为 NASA 认为它在 2025 年之后可能无法正常运行。</p><p> — 丹·库珀</p><p></p><p><em>您可以每天将这些报告直接发送到您的收件箱。</em><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/about/newsletter/"><em><ins>就在这里订阅吧！</ins></em></a></p><h3>您可能错过的最重要的故事</h3><p></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-games-for-ps5-playstation-5-171511880.html"><ins>2023 年最佳 PS5 游戏</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/marvels-visual-effects-workers-vote-to-join-a-union-123036176.html"><ins>漫威视觉特效工人投票成立工会</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gm-will-enable-vehicle-to-home-charging-on-all-ultium-based-evs-164248583.html"><ins>通用汽车将为所有基于 Ultium 的电动汽车提供车到户充电功能</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/valve-begins-selling-refurbished-steam-decks-for-around-20-percent-off-201808966.html"><ins>Valve 以约 20% 的折扣出售翻新的 Steam Deck</ins></a></p><p></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/why-humans-cant-use-natural-language-processing-to-speak-with-the-animals-143050169.html"><ins>为什么人类不能使用自然语言处理与动物交谈</ins></a></h2><h3>言语的复杂性与鸟鸣相比根本不算什么。</h3><p></p><p>如今的计算机虽然功能强大，但肯定足够聪明，可以解码简单的动物叫声吗？这是安德鲁·塔兰托拉最新专题的核心问题，它询问为什么<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/why-humans-cant-use-natural-language-processing-to-speak-with-the-animals-143050169.html"><ins>我们还没有用于动物语音的谷歌翻译</ins></a>。事实证明，就像我们耳朵听到的鸟叫声一样简单，它是有史以来最复杂的发声系统之一。请继续阅读，了解为什么事实上，<em>我们是</em>说实话的普通人，而不是我们的宠物。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/why-humans-cant-use-natural-language-processing-to-speak-with-the-animals-143050169.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-is-reportedly-testing-m3-chips-for-new-macs-arriving-this-fall-173457588.html"><ins>据报道，苹果正在为今年秋季上市的新款 Mac 测试 M3 芯片</ins></a></h2><h3>该公司可能希望加快新机器的发布时间表。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-is-reportedly-testing-m3-chips-for-new-macs-arriving-this-fall-173457588.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/290733c0-369c-11ee-b8ff-8e81b91997ca" style="height:416px;width:625px;" alt="图片：木桌上摆放着一台 MacBook Pro，旁边是老式闹钟和 Blue Yeti 麦克风。" data-uuid="bdd1c06d-763f-363a-941b-03511d34ee03"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">内森·英格拉汉姆 / Engadget 摄</div></figure></a><p>夜幕降临，苹果公司发布了新产品，其名称比目前销售的产品名称大一个整数。毫不奇怪，我们听说<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-is-reportedly-testing-m3-chips-for-new-macs-arriving-this-fall-173457588.html"><ins>M3 芯片目前正在接受测试，预计将在今年晚些时候进行更新</ins></a>。然而，可能令人惊讶的是，苹果可能会加快其发布时间表，以比现在更快地更新其计算机产品。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.e