强恐惧因素 - 这感觉与原始角色非常相关”， <em>《黎明杀机》</em>的游戏设计师 Janick Neveu 说道。 </p><div id="42c797345b424eb8a541f02c8d4e8562"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/E3XKx4KKCXU" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>你不必等待很长时间，就可以带着完全的恐惧在诺斯特罗莫残骸中漫步（这是一款完美的夜间游戏，对吧？），因为<em>《黎明杀机：异形》</em>将于 8 月 29 日开始跨平台发售。不耐烦？您已经可以下载游戏的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/dead-by-daylight-dating-sim-attack-on-titan-resident-evil-184556465.html">公共测试版本</a>并尽早尝试。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/alien-is-coming-to-dead-by-daylight-105502420.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/alien-is-coming-to-dead-by-daylight-105502420.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> c15384bf-4ccd-484c-9af9-26ef66b836be</guid><dc:creator>萨拉·菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 10:55:02 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691577487</ingested><modified> 2023-08-09T10:38:24+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="619" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/c6ac50c0-3696-11ee-beaf-6ec738f2cc7e" width="1100"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="619" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-